item.title: THM - Extending Your Network - Walkthrough
item.description: This series of walkthroughs aims to help out complete beginners with finishing the Pre Security Path on the TryHackMe (thm)1 website. It is based on the learning content provided in the Extending Your Network room. Task 1 - Introduction to Port Forwarding Check out how port forwarding works, and why it is so essential for network communications. Question 1: What is the name of the device that is used to configure port forwarding?
